PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?discipline ?disciplineLabel WHERE {
  ?discipline wdt:P31 wd:Q11862829 .
  ?discipline rdfs:label ?disciplineLabel .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?disciplineLabel ) , "linguistik" ) ) FILTER ( LANG( ?disciplineLabel ) = "de" )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?character ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?character wdt:P31 wd:Q95074 .
  ?character wdt:P21 wd:Q6581072 .
  ?character wdt:P106 wd:Q11397897 .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?year ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  wd:Q169452 p:P166 ?statement1 .
  ?statement1 ps:P166 wd:Q674359 ; pq:P585 ?year .
  wd:Q25369 p:P166 ?statement2 .
  ?statement2 ps:P166 wd:Q674359 ; pq:P585 ?year .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?movie ?movieLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q169604 wdt:P527 ?movie .
  ?movie rdfs:label ?movieLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?movieLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?team WHERE {
  wd:Q169452 p:P54 ?statement1 .
  ?statement1 ps:P54 ?team ; pq:P580 ?start1 ; pq:P582 ?end1 .
  wd:Q25369 p:P54 ?statement2 .
  ?statement2 ps:P54 ?team ; pq:P580 ?start2 ; pq:P582 ?end2 .
  BIND( xsd:integer ( SUBSTR( STR( ?start1 ) , 1 , 4 ) ) AS ?startYear1 ) .
  BIND( xsd:integer ( SUBSTR( STR( ?end1 ) , 1 , 4 ) ) AS ?endYear1 ) .
  BIND( xsd:integer ( SUBSTR( STR( ?start2 ) , 1 , 4 ) ) AS ?startYear2 ) .
  BIND( xsd:integer ( SUBSTR( STR( ?end2 ) , 1 , 4 ) ) AS ?endYear2 ) .
  FILTER ( ?startYear1 <= 2000 && ?endYear1 >= 2000 && ?startYear2 <= 2000 && ?endYear2 >= 2000 ) .
}
LIMIT 10
